        {
            "title": "葵涌貨櫃碼頭內運車翻側 司機一度被困 清醒獲救送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ac8c88d5c7954ab20bc648a59a43ee38/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051517352353602.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（15日）下午4時，警方接獲報案，指一輛內運車於葵涌8號貨櫃碼頭內吊運冷凍櫃，其間疑失控翻側，司機被困駕駛艙內。消防到場將司機救出，他報稱腳及膊頭受傷，清醒由救護車送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理，警方正調查事件原因，暫列「工業意外」處理。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250393/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"司機報稱腳及膊頭受傷，清醒由救護車送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/98a809631b1a8d91b61126d8143d3a37/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250515_172148925.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        司機報稱腳及膊頭受傷，清醒由救護車送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250396/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"司機報稱腳及膊頭受傷，清醒由救護車送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b4daf3521a5813aceeb67136c3b0d293/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250515_171438797.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"